content.content: Whoever asks this question is not a good interviewer. Unless it\'s an interview for mathematician....\n\nhttps://www.nayuki.io/page/smallest-enclosing-circle

Do not waste time on this problem unless you are preparing for some math/CS competitions. Won\'t be asked during an interview. Requires too many knowledge and formula. If you want to be a Ph.D. on this, go ahead and fight against it.
